('ONET-AGENTS_AND_BUSINESS_MANAGERS_OF_ARTISTS_PERFORME', 'source_onet_agents_and_business_managers_of_artists_performers_and_athletes', 'Agents and Business Managers of Artists, Performers, and Athletes', 'Agents and Business Managers of Artists, Performers, and Athletes is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Represent and promote artists, performers, and athletes in dealings with current or prospective employers. May handle contract negotiation and other business matters for clients.', ARRAY['Acquisition Agent','Advance Agent','Agent','Artist Manager','Artist Representative','Artist''s Manager','Artist''s Representative','Athlete Manager','Athlete Marketing Agent','Athletic Agent','Author''s Agent','Band Manager','Booker','Booking Agent','Booking Manager','Boxing Promoter','Business Agent','Business Manager','Circus Agent','Concert Promoter','Contracting Agent','Copyright Manager','Dramatic Agent','Entertainment Agent','Entertainment Specialist','Fight Manager','Film Booker','Jockey''s Agent','Literary Agent','Media Promoter','Modeling Agent','Music Agent','Music Promoter','Picture Booker','Print Agent','Promoter','Promotional Agent','Promotional Marketing Agent','Promotional Representative','Repertoire Manager','Sports Agent','Talent Acquisition Team','Talent Agent','Talent Booker','Talent Manager','Talent Representative','Talent Solutions Manager','Theatrical Agent','Touring Agent','Touring Production Manager']::text[], ARRAY['Agents and Business Managers of Artists, Performers, and Athletes','Acquisition Agent','Advance Agent','Agent','Artist Manager','Artist Representative','Artist''s Manager','Artist''s Representative','Athlete Manager','Athlete Marketing Agent','Athletic Agent','Author''s Agent','Band Manager','Booker','Booking Agent','Booking Manager','Boxing Promoter','Business Agent','Business Manager','Circus Agent','Concert Promoter','Contracting Agent','Copyright Manager