('ONET-WHOLESALE_AND_RETAIL_BUYERS_EXCEPT_FARM_PRODUCTS', 'source_onet_wholesale_and_retail_buyers_except_farm_products', 'Wholesale and Retail Buyers, Except Farm Products', 'Wholesale and Retail Buyers, Except Farm Products is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Buy merchandise or commodities, other than farm products, for resale to consumers at the wholesale or retail level, including both durable and nondurable goods. Analyze past buying trends, sales records, price, and quality of merchandise to determine value and yield. Select, order, and authorize payment for merchandise according to contractual agreements. May conduct meetings with sales personnel and introduce new products. May negotiate contracts. Includes assistant wholesale and retail buyers of nonfarm products.', ARRAY['Acquisition Specialist','Art Dealer','Buyer','Buying Professional','Category Planner','Commodity Buyer','Contract Sourcing Specialist','Contracts Specialist','Exporter','Fashion Buyer','Fur Buyer','Gold Buyer','Grocery Buyer','Internal Wholesaler','Merchandise Buyer','Merchandise for Resale Purchasing Agent','Merchandise Planner','Merchant','Planner','Print Buyer','Procurement Buyer','Procurement Officer','Procurement Representative','Procurement Specialist','Purchaser','Purchasing Agent','Purchasing Buyer','Purchasing Coordinator','Purchasing Specialist','Purveyor','Resident Buyer','Retail Buyer','Sourcing Analyst','Sourcing Specialist','Strategic Sourcing Specialist','Sustainability Purchasing Agent','Technical Buyer','Technical Sourcing Specialist','Tie Buyer','Trader','Tradesman','Wholesale and Retail Merchant','Wholesale Buyer']::text[], ARRAY['Wholesale and Retail Buyers, Except Farm Products','Acquisition Specialist','Art Dealer','Buyer','Buying Professional','Category Planner','Commodity Buyer','Contract Sourcing Specialist','Contracts Specialist','Exporter','Fashion Buyer','Fur Buyer','Gold Buyer