('ONET-PURCHASING_AGENTS_EXCEPT_WHOLESALE_RETAIL_AND_FA', 'source_onet_purchasing_agents_except_wholesale_retail_and_farm_products', 'Purchasing Agents, Except Wholesale, Retail, and Farm Products', 'Purchasing Agents, Except Wholesale, Retail, and Farm Products is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Purchase machinery, equipment, tools, parts, supplies, or services necessary for the operation of an establishment. Purchase raw or semifinished materials for manufacturing. May negotiate contracts.', ARRAY['Buyer','Contract Administrator (Contract Admin)','Contract Analyst','Contract Specialist','Contractor Buyer','Contracts Manager','Equipment, Supplies, and Tools Purchasing Agent','Fuel Agent','Fuel Buyer','General Purchasing Agent','Log Buyer','Lumber Buyer','Media Buyer','Ore Buyer','Price Analyst','Print Buyer','Procurement Agent','Procurement Analyst','Procurement and Contracting Administrator (Procurement and Contracting Admin)','Procurement and Contracting Buyer','Procurement Coordinator','Procurement Engineer','Procurement Official','Procurement Specialist','Pulpwood Buyer','Pulpwood Contractor','Purchaser','Purchasing Administrator (Purchasing Admin)','Purchasing Agent','Purchasing and Contracts Coordinator','Purchasing Coordinator','Purchasing Specialist','Railroad Purchasing Agent','Replenishment Buyer','Sourcing Specialist','Subcontract Administrator (Subcontract Admin)','Subcontract Associate','Timber Buyer','Tools, Supplies, and Equipment Purchasing Agent']::text[], ARRAY['Purchasing Agents, Except Wholesale, Retail, and Farm Products','Buyer','Contract Administrator (Contract Admin)','Contract Analyst','Contract Specialist','Contractor Buyer','Contracts Manager','Equipment, Supplies, and Tools Purchasing Agent','Fuel Agent','Fuel Buyer','General Purchasing Agent','Log Buyer','Lumber Buyer','Media Buyer','Ore Buyer','Price Analyst','Print Buyer','Procurement Agent','Procur